   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>Well, we now have an IRC bot named sufjan! And he takes minutes in MediaWiki format!

The only thing is that he can't upload them to the wiki because of the
CAPTCHA... is there a way to maybe disable the CAPTCHA for certain IPs, for
example the same IP as the wiki itself is running on? =D

(Also, he would be uploading them with no account, so the meeting page creations
would be tied to the OpenHatch server's IP. I am not sure if we should give him
one, as then it is possible for someone to take the same name on Django and
steal the account...)</pre>
   </td>
  </tr>
 
 
  <tr>
   <th><a href="msg1003">msg1003 (view)</a></th>
