  <tr>
   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>I think I will go with your suggested option: a supybot instance with the
MeetBot plugin. Plus this means we now have an IRC bot with heaps of plugins!
^_^ (including a standard channel logger, but it only logs to flat file, so not
nearly as awesome as myone logging to MySQL and generating live web pages ;D )

I noticed that the MeetBot plugin can be configured to output in a variety of
formats, including a MediaWiki format (.mw), but it doesn't support uploading it
to MediaWiki. This could be useful? (It's already suggested as a wish, so if we
can find or write MediaWiki-uploading code in Python then we could get it
integrated in.)</pre>
   </td>
  </tr>
 
 
