    <pre>I just spent a while finding the old IRC topic, and I would instead rather have
a bot that let us temporarily change the topic to one most useful for a meeting,
and then restore it.

Maybe <a href="http://wiki.debian.org/MeetBot">http://wiki.debian.org/MeetBot</a> could help.</pre>
